<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two adjoining pieces of the lower part of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs>; traces of figures above.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in four lines on a broad lower border; the text must have begun on an upper feature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025</measure>; ligatures: l. 2,  <foreign lang="grc">ΝΜ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">ΝΗ</foreign>; l. 3,  <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign> (twice), <foreign lang="grc">ΜΜ</foreign>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date>
 (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
